  "limitations": [
    "All metrics are post-hoc diagnostics on five already-consumed BTCUSDT calibration days and cannot establish out-of-sample profitability.",
    "The source has event-level best-bid-offer and trades but no full Level-2 queue, so maker fills, queue priority, hidden liquidity, and full market impact cannot be estimated.",
    "One-second causal features and five-second decisions do not represent sub-second alpha generation even though execution quotes are sampled from a certified 100 ms BBO path.",
    "Five daily blocks provide weak regime and daily-stability evidence; placebo ranks are descriptive and do not authorize formal multiple-testing significance claims.",
    "Overlapping event outcomes are not executable trades or a portfolio backtest; the nonoverlapping subset is only a dependence robustness diagnostic.",
    "ETHUSDT and SOLUSDT require separately certified corpora and are not covered by this BTCUSDT diagnostic.",
    "A zero-latency counterfactual estimates historical quote-path latency drag and is not an achievable execution claim.",
    "No result from this round permits leverage, order placement, model promotion, or trading authority."
  ],
